<paragraph id="05D9F240E8D267E0849159ED8DA40279" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">Zweifelhafte Strauchscharte</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="B64FCADE6E345380567FDAA366825180" pageId="null" pageNumber="431" type="description">
<paragraph id="E7684C3905C19A4757D1390CF650C08D" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">
10-30 cm hoch. Stengel bis unter die 
<normalizedToken id="3F74D8A6486E693CBEB0D1C7F6DF2C96" originalValue="Köpfe" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">Koepfe</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="A81118BB424581DFF2D2C7356B45C671" originalValue="beblättert" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">beblaettert</normalizedToken>
. 
<emphasis id="7FB9242A29A8AF95DCFD342358B2A9B3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">
<normalizedToken id="0D20BEA75C9B131BEFCD39EF02F32D9C" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
sehr schmal lanzettlich
</emphasis>
, bis 4 cm lang und 0,4 cm breit, 
<emphasis id="0D10A54725C09C2963050A9F500F5973" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">am Rande nach unten gerollt.</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="DEB052ED880C1DC339F1DDC34782FDCF" originalValue="Köpfe" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">Koepfe</normalizedToken>
im Durchmesser 0,5-1 cm. 
<normalizedToken id="A55B14AC756BC5D774AB1502DB01D4AF" originalValue="Hülle" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">Huelle</normalizedToken>
1,5-2 cm lang, 
<normalizedToken id="B273C14861C9652A3B4AB3BC47DEB26B" originalValue="rötlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">roetlich</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="ACD5E927193EE0C9E93CB320695E41D2" originalValue="Hüllblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">Huellblaetter</normalizedToken>
spitz, gegen die Spitze auf dem 
<normalizedToken id="36EADE641D5D5A569E66AA8B459EFE09" originalValue="Rücken" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">Ruecken</normalizedToken>
zerstreut filzig behaart. Kronen purpurn. 
<normalizedToken id="476286DC92CD190A62C7BA31F7F01CF7" originalValue="Früchte" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">Fruechte</normalizedToken>
5-7 mm lang. 
<emphasis id="041B845EF5BB0137F8A9A449DCB0E557" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">
<taxonomicName id="B1D9E15A60D8749930B287478BFB7BC2" class="Insecta" family="Miridae" genus="Pappus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="431" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Pappus</taxonomicName>
ca. 20 mm lang.
</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="36AD1AB12FD4C9DBF254B9E3C1E88A37" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C04511942B9A26013273DFEACC084608" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">
<emphasis id="5A852A7F3BC866AFC13F6D28755B4026" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="A613A0C5CE17F87B2F8E71D9B30E1C33" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">30:</emphasis>
Material aus den Alpes Maritimes (Guinochet und Logeois 1962).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="69CCE045C1ADE8BB0B4EBA7C8590C2E1" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">
<emphasis id="6D37892FA9963E8B59BD02EF9AF0E46E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin. Steinige, trockene 
<normalizedToken id="E5759BF1A6E3AAE685933B2E4084A857" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen Lagen. Felsensteppen, steinige 
<normalizedToken id="C1472DC3F01AEC27EE4CA2271B483790" originalValue="Hänge" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">Haenge</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4C28F0575901D53EE527C96EEF8366D3" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">
<emphasis id="F388C9ADD2F9C5652BAD6ACD798D26D3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">Verbreitung. Westmediterrane Pflanze:</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="74B2B312EB578142F6B556F2FAD68875" originalValue="Nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">Nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis 
<normalizedToken id="5CEE18C3C28CCA9F1041AACAA7861349" originalValue="Südalpen" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">Suedalpen</normalizedToken>
; ost- und 
<normalizedToken id="90D9FDC3D3FFC834F1B9E7339244E4EB" originalValue="südwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">suedwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Dalmatien, Abruzzen, Sardinien, 
<normalizedToken id="831339D62BE44B2E974C7D1D0D179015" originalValue="Südspanien" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">Suedspanien</normalizedToken>
, Marokko. - Im Gebiet: 
<normalizedToken id="DDB141B65584446C5C7BDE54B763FA6B" originalValue="Südöstliche" pageId="null" pageNumber="431">Suedoestliche</normalizedToken>
Bergamasker Alpen (zwischen Adrara und Foresto).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
